## How to Run

```bash
# Mock mode (no API keys needed)
python main.py --agent 2 --mock --output agent2_output.json

# With Agent 1 live context
python main.py --agent 2 --agent1-json live_output.json

# Run tests
pytest tests/test_agent2.py -v
```
